===Etymology 1===
From {{inh|en|enm|fleute}}, {{m|enm|floute}}, {{m|enm|flote}}, from {{der|en|fro|flaute}}, {{m|fro|fleÃ¼te}}, from {{der|en|oc-pro-old|flaut|flaÃ¼t}}, of {{unc|en|nocap=1}} origin. Perhaps ultimately from three possibilities:
* Blend of Provencal {{m|oc|flaujol|t=flageolet}} + {{m|oc|laÃ¼t|t=[[lute]]}}
* From Latin {{m|la|flÄtus|t=blowing}}, from {{m|la|flÄre|t=to blow}}
* Imitative.
